title: simplehuman compact sensor pump
description: Our touch-free compact sensor pump is the most efficient and easy way to wash your hands — no germs or smudges left behind. Perfect for small sinks or countertops, its high-efficiency pump mechanism with speed dispense provides fast and accurate dispensing in just 0.2 seconds. A silicone valve prevents messy drips and clogs, while the wide opening makes refills fast, easy and mess-free.
